<p><a href="#sdfootnote6anc" name="sdfootnote6sym">6</a> Kletowski explained them in a sense that was slightly closer to Królikiewicz: <em>Pracuję dla przyszłości</em> “depicts the direction that can be followed not only by art, but also by the spiritual development of the nation.” Marecki and Kletowski, <em>Królikiewicz</em>, 344.</p>
