<p><a href="#sdfootnote14anc" name="sdfootnote14sym">14</a> Determining the temporal frames of the Polish transformation poses considerable problems to researchers. <em>Duchologia polska</em> concerns merely a fragment of that process, distinguished primarily because of the “phantom-like” character of the phenomena highlighted by the author. See: Olga Drenda, <em>Duchologia polska </em>(Warsaw: Karakter, 2016), 13–14. Problems with establishing the watershed moments of the transformation and the very definition thereof were discussed by Magda Szcześniak in: <em>Normy widzialności. </em><em>Tożsamość w czasach transformacji</em> (Warsaw: Bęc Zmiana, 2016), 16–19.</p>
